<body lang=EN-US style='tab-interval:.5in'>

<div class=Section1>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>ISP
120<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><b><span
style='font-size:16.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Tips for working with
Percentages and Comparisons</span></b><span style='font-size:16.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>General
advice for solving a problem<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<ol style='margin-top:0in' start=1 type=1>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Identify the type of
     problem and choose the correct equation.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> 
     </span>Absolute difference?<span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> 
     </span>Percent change?<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>Proportion
     of?<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Identify the
     variables.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>What is the original
     amount being compared to?<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">   </span>What is
     the new amount that is being described in relation to the original amount?<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Plug the values into
     the formula and solve.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ol>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Also
notice whether the problem requires you to calculate an answer just once, or
whether it has 2 or more steps (eg: decreased 50% then increased 70%).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b><span style='font-size:16.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Tips
for specific problem types and formulas:<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><b><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Absolute Change or Absolute
Difference<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Absolute
change = new amount - original amount<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Phrases
that typically signal a comparison involving absolute change or absolute
difference:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<ul style='margin-top:0in' type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l6 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>&quot;how many more
     than&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l6 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>&quot;as much more
     than&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l6 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>&quot;A has how much
     more than B&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Identifying
the &quot;new&quot; and &quot;original&quot; values:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<ul style='margin-top:0in' type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>the new amount is
     usually the subject of the sentence<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>the original amount
     will usually be the object of a preposition like &quot;than&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>&quot;(new amount) is x
     more than (original amount).&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>&quot;(new amount) is x
     less than (base amount).&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><b><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Relative Change or Relative
Difference</span></b><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Proportion
change = (absolute change) / (original amount)</span></b><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'> = (new - original) /
original = (new / original) - 1<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Phrases
that typically signal a comparison involving proportion change or proportion
difference:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<ul style='margin-top:0in' type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l0 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>&quot;A is x times more
     than B&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l0 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>&quot;increased by a
     factor of x&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l0 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>&quot;A is half as much
     as B&quot; (or some other fraction as much)<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Percent
Change = (proportion change) * 100%</span></b><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'> = ((new - original) / original) * 100%<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Phrases
that typically signal a comparison involving percentage change or percentage
difference:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<ul style='margin-top:0in' type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l1 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>&quot;A is x% more than
     B&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l1 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>&quot;A is x% less than
     B&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l1 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>&quot;increased by
     x%&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l1 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>&quot;decreased by
     x%&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><b><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Relative Size or Relative
Amount<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Proportion
of = new / original<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Phrases
that typically signal a comparison involving proportion of:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<ul style='margin-top:0in' type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l8 level1 lfo6;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>&quot;A is x times as
     much as B&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l8 level1 lfo6;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>&quot;A is half as much
     as B&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Percentage
of = (proportion of) * 100%</span></b><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt'> = (new - original) * 100%<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Phrases
that typically signal a comparison involving percentage of:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<ul style='margin-top:0in' type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l7 level1 lfo7;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>&quot;A is x% of
     B&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l7 level1 lfo7;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>&quot;x% of A are
     B&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><b><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Percent Difference vs.
Percentage Point Difference</span></b><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>&quot;Percent
higher&quot; means a <u>relative</u> change comparison (percent change or
percent difference)<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>&quot;Percentage
points higher&quot; means an <u>absolute</u> difference or absolute change.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>Example:<span
