 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l3 level1 lfo9;tab-stops:list .5in'><span
     style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt'>B is 2 percentage
     points higher than A.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><i>absolute
     change = new - original = 12% - 10% = 2%</i><o:p></o:p></span></li>
